## Claude Code Notes

The operational instructions for the Groundwork checkout live in `AGENTS.md` at the
root of the Groundwork repo.

On a managed machine, find that checkout with:

```bash
source="$(chezmoi source-path)"
if [ "$(basename "$source")" = "home" ]; then dirname "$source"; else printf '%s\n' "$source"; fi
```

Read the repo-root `AGENTS.md` first and follow it. Do not add shared policy
here; update `AI_THESIS.md` for the north star or `AGENTS.md` for operational
repo instructions so Codex, Claude Code, and other coding agents stay aligned.

